parameters: Clea: Sophia-san, you're drinking too much.

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, it's so fun when I'm in front of
Clea-chan.
Thief Nora: I didn't regain any of my memories at all...

Mage Relm: The real Clato has disappeared too! Maybe this
person pretending to be him was actually a fraudster!
Thief Nora: Somehow, I feel refreshed in my body!

Mage Relm: That might be the effect of the Memory Candle for
me too...
Thief Nora: ...It's not going so well, huh.

Mage Relm: There's no need to feel down! The genius of the
academy will definitely help you regain your memories.
Thief Nora: Yes, I'm looking forward to it!

Thank you for accepting the invitation, servant of the
licentious noble Eshis.

My master, the licentious noble Eshis, will surely be
delighted as well.

Clea: Can you prove that the sender of this invitation is
the real licentious noble Eshis?

Servant of the licentious noble Eshis: To address that
doubt, first we will give you 50,000G as an advance payment.
Clea: Such a large sum of money...

Servant of the licentious noble Eshis: Before you meet our
master, the licentious noble Eshis, I apologize for the
rudeness, but we have prepared several tests to determine if
you are worthy.

Servant of the licentious noble Eshis: Each time you pass a
test, we will give you a reward on the spot.

Clea: If we fail to pass the test, can we understand that we
will return what we have received?

Servant of the licentious noble Eshis: There is no need for
that. It is a gesture of sincerity for your trouble.

Servant of the licentious noble Eshis: Therefore, you can
stop the tests at any time without any problem.

Servant of the licentious noble Eshis: I promise that when
you pass all the tests, our master will respond with the
utmost sincerity.
Clea: Alright, please tell me the details of the first test.

Servant of the licentious noble Eshis: There is an island
called the Prostitution Island in Mucos. Please find a way
to reach it by any means necessary.

Servant of the licentious noble Eshis: I will be waiting for
you on Prostitution Island.

Servant of the licentious noble Eshis: I look forward to
meeting you.

Please note that this is a special quest directive and fast
travel is not possible.
